title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - World Update VII Australia - Photogrammetry Adelaide
description:
Last week World Update VII Australia was released. In this video we will do our seventh flight above Australia and we are going to visit Adelaide. We will take of from Adelaide International and will fly towards the city center where are a lot of 3D buildings have been added. Once we visited the city center we will fly to the North and visit the harbor part of the city. As final destination we will try to land on one of the other airports close to the city, if I will succeed ... have a look yourself ;-)
